snippet.title: A look into... Trailer
snippet.description:
In a peaceful yet mysterious world, you discover a myriad of wildlife, collect materials and recipes to help the communities you encounter, find new skins for yourself and maybe figure out what is going on in this strange land, and your role in it all.

Wishlist on steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2267140/A_look_into/

Trailer made with https://www.youtube.com/@pixel.3d.x
